<p><cs><col><b>Pomarine jager</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>a North
Atlantic jager (<spn>Stercorarius pomarinus</spn>) having the elongated
middle tail feathers obtuse. The adult is black.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
